{"text_id":181486,"tokens":["We"," present"," an"," iterative"," method"," to"," compute"," the"," sign"," function"," of"," a"," non","-","Her","mitian"," matrix","."," This"," method"," is"," based"," on"," the"," contour"," integral"," representation"," of"," the"," sign"," function"," and"," the"," application"," of"," the"," Cauchy"," integral"," formula","."," The"," method"," is"," particularly"," useful"," for"," the"," computation"," of"," the"," sign"," function"," of"," the"," overlap"," Dirac"," operator"," at"," nonzero"," chemical"," potential",","," which"," is"," a"," key"," quantity"," in"," the"," study"," of"," Quantum"," Chrom","odynamics"," (","QCD",")"," at"," finite"," density","."," We"," demonstrate"," the"," efficiency"," and"," accuracy"," of"," the"," method"," through"," numerical"," experiments","."," The"," results"," show"," that"," the"," method"," is"," robust"," and"," reliable",","," and"," it"," can"," be"," applied"," to"," large","-","scale"," problems"," in"," QCD","."," Furthermore",","," we"," discuss"," the"," potential"," applications"," of"," the"," method"," in"," other"," areas"," of"," computational"," physics","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4","label":1}